  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK919">
<l>varaivilā māṇiḻaiyār meṉṟōḷ puraiyilāp </l>
<l>pūriyarka ḷāḻu maḷaṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The delicate shoulders of prostitutes with excellent jewels are a hell into which are plunged the ignorant base.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
